###############################################################################
Compiling the LabVolt library on generic linux

Install the following using pacman/apt-get/yum/rpm/etc.:
gcc/g++
make
libudev
	libudev is likely part of another package
	On Fedora 18 it is part of systemd
libudev-devel
	libudev-devel is likely part of another package
	On Fedora 18 it is part of systemd-devel

cd into the lib directory and type make. If no errors popped up and liblabvolt.a appeared in the lib directory, you're done!

###############################################################################
Some additional information is available in 5150-Software-API.pdf.

